40ea1f48-12b8-46cb-b2f2-eafd29de3272.name: sql
40ea1f48-12b8-46cb-b2f2-eafd29de3272.value:
select
   p.first_name /* denormalized_person.first_name */
   , p.last_name /* denormalized_person.last_name */
   , p.gender /* denormalized_person.gender */
   , a.address1 /* denormalized_person.address1 */
   , a.address2 /* denormalized_person.address2 */
   , a.city /* denormalized_person.city */
   , a.state /* denormalized_person.state */
   , a.postal_code /* denormalized_person.postal_code */
   , hp.phone_number /* denormalized_person.home_phone */
   , cp.phone_number /* denormalized_person.work_phone */
   , wp.phone_number /* denormalized_person.cell_phone */
from
   person p
   left outer join address a
      on p.id = a.person_id
   left outer join phone hp
      on p.id = hp.person_id
      and hp.phone_type = 'Home'
   left outer join phone cp
      on p.id = cp.person_id
      and cp.phone_type = 'Cell'
   left outer join phone wp
      on p.id = wp.person_id
      and wp.phone_type = 'Work'
